                      <span>10</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1998-05-30</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book gives the reader a good general overview of the development of modern military history. There are many good essays on (in my opinion too many) the 17th and 18th century. The modern reader concerned with more recent developments might find the last part of the book more beneficial</span>
                  
              
